text.tspan: DURING TRANSPORT, THE OCTAWEB IS MOUNTED TO THE TRAILER
FAIRINGS LARGE ENOUGH TO FIT A BUS
NEARLY AS TALL AS THE FALCON 1
ALL OF THE COMPONENTS FOR THE FALCON 9 ARE SHIPPED TO THE LAUNCH SITE
ON U.S. HIGHWAYS. THE FALCON 9 WAS DESIGNED FROM THE START TO FIT U.S. ROADS.
DURING THE TRANSPORTATION OF FALCON 9 STAGES, THEY ARE PRESSURIZED WITH
NITROGEN AND COVERED IN A CUSTOM-MADE BLACK PLASTIC WRAP TO KEEP THEM
CLEAN AND FREE OF FOREIGN OBJECTS.
